Key Features

Infrastructure as Code (IaC): Automated provisioning and management of cloud infrastructure.

CI/CD Pipelines: Continuous integration and delivery for seamless deployments.

Monitoring and Logging: Real-time performance tracking and error logging.

Security and Compliance: Vulnerability scanning, access control, and encryption.

Backup and Recovery: Disaster recovery strategies and automated backups.

Automation Scripts: Deployment, performance testing, and security auditing.

Microservices Architecture: Modular and scalable design for cloud applications.
